<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I don&apos;t think so Harriette. I haven&apos;t read this one yet but I have read all the others and even though the author might repeat what happened previousl<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I don't think so Harriette. I haven't read this one yet but I have read all the others and even though the author might repeat what happened previously I think there would be too much detail and events for you to keep track and read it enjoyably. Each book follows a different couple and this one continues the story of the couple in the very first book <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/42899.Dark_Lover">https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/4...</a> . I would recommend you read the first book either way,it's a pretty good series.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
