<a href="/questions/2026047-is-it-okay-for-a-14-year-old-girl-i-m">Is it okay for a 14 year old girl? I&#39;m very open in general. I don&#39;t mind mild sex scenes etc. I don&#39;t want her reading anything too explicit though.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_2026047'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F21911707-the-king">like</a></span>

