</a><br><br>If you loved the earlier stories which were filled with passion and romance and <i>happily ever afters</i> obtained through faith, trust, honor, dignity, soul cleansing pain, and making compromises for the one you love because you love them above all else... you'll be happy to know that The King has all of these things, and more!<br><br>And that quote up there... "Let yourself go and I shall catch you..." applies to so many people and situations in this story - trust, faith, hope... beautiful things.<br><br><i>Full review to come.........</i></span>
