<span id="freeTextContainer3861850540207963239">January 15, 2018~ (Audiobook) Reread <br/><br/>It’s been awhile since I’ve read this, I was getting twitchy and needed a Wrath fix. I’m still completely and throughly devoted to Wrath!!<br/><a href='http://s1186.photobucket.com/user/dshewey1/media/Smileys/heart_turn_love_zps68f9eb25.gif.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
