 for Dallas at last, until a stage accident sends her home and shatters her dreams. Blow after blow she fights the hand of fate. Is she destined to lose out in life? Hope, dreams, and love seem to be just out of reach. Every girl dreams of a happy ending. Will a spontaneous card reading reveal her destiny?Dallas Fortune has the best Fairy Godmother in country music history. Will she help make Dallas’ dreams come true?\n\nIs the future among the stars, in the cards or locked in your heart?\n\nFortune Calling is the first story in The Fortune Series. Set in contemporary Nashville and rural Tennessee, the series chronicles the life and loves of Dallas Fortune. \n\nThis story was featured as the #1 recommendation on Amazon\'s Recommended Reading List for Literature &amp; Fiction, Wednesday February 12, 2014. \n\nTAGS: Fiction, Country Music, Nashville, Tennessee, Guitars, Short story, Contemporary\n\n© 2014 Ra Jones Publishing\nCover by Robin Ludwig Designs<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"8769827834853996520\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'22_book_20516112\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"35UqwkAWwxaY4AxLdfbIoZd5Oi78bCzuFAyFNU5MJBvzXxu01ApdKpO4SElt0Af+7ax3y8+YcUVr5eyLZFlwdg==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"20516112\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"22_book_20516112\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n